            		<li id="fn2"><em>Africa Remix: Contemporary Art of a Continent</em>, held from May 27 to August 31, 2006.<a href="#ref2">↩</a></li>
            		<li id="fn3">Kraus, RK; <em>Brushes with Power</em>, University of California Press, Berkeley, 1991, p 27.<a href="#ref3">↩</a></li>
            	</ol>            
            </div>
