                <h4>About the Author</h4>
                <p>Born in 1975 in Guelma, Algeria. He was educated in Cameroon, Belgium and Japan. He received his BA from the <span class="sc">ERG</span> in Brussels, his MA in traditional Japanese calligraphy from Gakugei University in Tokyo and his PhD in contemporary art from the Tokyo National University of Fine Arts and Music. He has been based in Tokyo since 2001. He has exhibited internationally and held artist residencies in New York, Jordan, Israel, Iran and China. You can read more about his work on <a href="http://transcri.be" class="out">transcri.be</a>.</p>
